        <Parent_String>stacks (piping) [300052614], piping (plumbing system components) [300052572], plumbing and stormwater system components [300052523], system components [300242031], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
